  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h1>Your Ultimate Size Guide for Rings, Necklaces, and Bracelets</h1>
        <p>Finding the perfect fit for your jewelry ensures both comfort and style. <a href = https://www.lucirajewelry.com/ target="_blank">Lucira Jewelry's</a> size guide offers step-by-step instructions to help you measure rings, bracelets, bangles, and necklaces with ease. Let's find the perfect fit for you!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ring Size Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>Ring Size Guide</h2>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="custom-text-column">
            <p><strong>Method 1:</strong> Measure an Existing Ring</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Select a ring that fits your desired finger.</li>
              <li>Measure its inner diameter using a flexible measuring tape.</li>
              <li>Use our conversion chart to find your ring size.</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
          <div class="custom-image-column">
            <img src="{{ 'ring-scale.webp' | asset_url }}" title="Elegant Jewelry" alt="Elegant Jewelry" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
          <div class="text-column">
              <p><strong>Method 2:</strong> Wrap a paper strip or string around your finger, mark and measure it, then refer to our size chart.</p>
              <ol>
                <li>Measure in the evening for better accuracy.</li>
                <li>Warm hands give more accurate measurements.</li>
                <li>Avoid alcohol or salt before measuring.</li>
                <li>If your knuckle is larger, measure both base and knuckle.</li>
              </ol>
          </div>
          <div class="video-column">
            <video controls autoplay loop muted>
              <source src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/b6bd45e165384f7bb50a9598b5986822.mp4" type="video/mp4">
              Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
          </div>
        </div>


        <br>
        <p>Tips for Accurate Ring Measurement:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Measure your finger in the evening when it's slightly larger.</li>
          <li>Ensure your hands are warm, as cold temperatures can shrink your fingers.</li>
          <li>Avoid measuring after consuming alcohol or salty foods, as they can cause swelling.</li>
          <li>If your knuckle is larger than the base of your finger, measure both and choose a size that slides on comfortably.</li>
        </ul>
        <h5><strong>Need Help?</strong><a href="https://lucirajewelry.com/pages/contact-us"> Contact our team</a> for personalized assistance </h5>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

