  <!-- Bracelet Size Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>Bracelet Size Guide</h2>
        <p>A well-fitted bracelet enhances both comfort and elegance. Here's how to measure your wrist accurately:</p>
        <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Measure Your Wrist</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Wrap a flexible tape measure around your wrist where the bracelet will sit.</li>
          <li>If using a piece of string, mark the meeting point and measure it against a ruler.</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Determine Your Preferred Fit</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Add 1 inch for a snug fit if your bracelet has a clasp.</li>
          <li>For bangles and cuffs, measure the widest part of your hand to ensure an easy slide-on fit.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

