          <p>Choosing the right necklace length enhances your personal style and outfit. Here's a quick step-by-step guide:</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Wrap a flexible tape measure or piece of string around your neck where you'd like the necklace to sit.</li>
              <li>Add 2 inches for a comfortable fit or 4 inches for a looser drape.</li>
              <li>For chokers, measure the exact circumference of your neck and add 0.5 inches for comfort.</li>
