  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>Necklace Length Guide</h2>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>14"</strong> Choker: Sits snugly at the base of the neck. Ideal for off-shoulder and V-neck outfits.</li>
          <li><strong>16"</strong> Collarbone Length: Versatile and perfect for layering with pendants.</li>
          <li><strong>18"</strong> Princess Length (Most Popular!): Sits just below the collarbone, complementing most outfits.</li>
          <li><strong>20"</strong> Matinee Length: Falls around the top of the bust, perfect for professional wear.</li>
